The ECLiPt Mirroring Tool (or EMirror for short) is a full features
FTP-mirroring software with nice logfiles.

Features:
   * Mirrors FTP-sites
   * Gets only the latest version of files (e.g. kernel)
   * HTML, PHP or Text logfiles (Example)
   * multi-threaded
   * Regular expressions for including / excluding files
   * Mechanisms for not getting really old files
   * Support for most kinds of ftp-daemons (including EPLF)
   * Support of re-get

WWW: http://sourceforge.net/projects/emirror/
